Insider Activity


Individual




Pierre M. Omidyar



Mr. Pierre M. Omidyar is Co-Founder at Omidyar Network LLC, Chairman at eBay, Inc. and Chief Executive Officer at Peer News LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Tufts University, Santa Fe Institute, Seesmic, Inc., Punahou School, and Roshan Cultural Heritage Institute.
Prior to co-founding Omidyar Newtwork LLC in June 2004, Mr. Omidyar was previously employed as Co-Founder by eShop, Inc. He also served on the board at Meetup, Inc.
Mr. Omidyar received his undergraduate degree from Tufts University.



