Pierre Omidyar - Wikipedia






















 






Pierre Omidyar

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Pierre Omidyar



Omidyar in 2007



Born
(1967-06-21) June 21, 1967 (age 50)
Paris, France


Residence
Henderson, Nevada, United States[1]


Nationality
Iranian-American


Occupation
Founder of eBay
Founder of Honolulu Civil Beat
Founder of Ulupono Initiative
